{"tid":611122,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[純分享]慢煮雞脾排","createTime":"2018-03-30T15:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T02:20:16.000Z","uid":146241,"like":33,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"188179558364d1ac69a877771354760c49bcba25","tid":611122,"uid":146241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"話說我老婆近排買左支慢煮棒<br />\n今日整左個慢煮雞脾排<br />\n想同大家分享下<br />\n我地都係新手<br />\n煮得唔好唔好屌咁大力<br />\n<br />\n雞脾排係上網買既<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eEjBS65.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeEjBS65.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=1rRYkwox2c35Iw131GJFoozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=933eacbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/eEjBS65.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n用沙薑粉+孜然粉醃 (因為屋企得尼D)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WpBnUvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWpBnUvG.jpg&h=43135aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HZFtb8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHZFtb8g.jpg&h=d0427b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後入袋, 倒D油入去<br />\n用75度慢煮45分鐘<br />\n雞都係熟D好<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TO9DETN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTO9DETN.jpg&h=ba768529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢煮完就變成咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2lcw7IE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2lcw7IE.jpg&h=55401528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後大火煎<br />\n只係煎雞皮個面<br />\n目的係令佢脆口<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ESyKEJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FESyKEJW.jpg&h=cb1bb7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約煎2-3分鐘就ok<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JCIAAt8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJCIAAt8.jpg&h=39ddc246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼個時候準備配菜<br />\n番茄仔焗10分鐘<br />\n啡菇焗15分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qHNA0a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqHNA0a9.jpg&h=7d140235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外係超市買左D甜粟<br />\n慢煮完個雞脾排就再慢煮佢<br />\n落D牛油85度慢煮30分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fA8EsKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfA8EsKS.jpg&h=a129c10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攪點!上碟!<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FT16X3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFT16X3y.jpg&h=ab7c450c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VTG1tA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVTG1tA2.jpg&h=d0419e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能煮耐左D, 或者煎既時候壓佢<br />\n中間冇想像中咁juicy<br />\n不過成碟野都好好食~ 多謝收睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qcpsgcQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqcpsgcQ.jpg&h=d28def1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7780276252f524cad4c5efa2a440e73de813c5a9","tid":611122,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"8cf34a946bb678a93664130613477c90625d3156","tid":611122,"uid":107879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"6acf49d580d0d142841e02560572d2bb3e222653","tid":611122,"uid":44454,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"雞本身就唔韌，走去慢煮又殺唔死啲菌，根本上多餘"},{"pid":"db8ad893d435c9ea3936dc9bde5155d6e0833cd0","tid":611122,"uid":81698,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"65度45分鐘就夠75度太高<br />\n<br />\n煎果陣壓佢一定流失好多肉汁<br />\n<br />\n最理想係KEEP係袋入面到你搞掂晒D配菜先大火煎雞皮脆身即上<br />\n<br />\nBTW雞脾扒真係唔洗慢煮 是鳩旦煎啦屌<br />\n雞胸就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057b491a5d2ebabc1cc947b9b0fce4edbddd3c93","tid":611122,"uid":178303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"雞脾都要慢煮 冇諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3740eff04bad94bd09518faf5b3d8ad713bff0","tid":611122,"uid":5220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6acf49d580d0d142841e02560572d2bb3e222653","tid":611122,"uid":44454,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"雞本身就唔韌，走去慢煮又殺唔死啲菌，根本上多餘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"除左雞胸<br />\n其他部位都唔值得慢煮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99502cfa1d9a3cd277d6ab4a0d1a0818fd1de52","tid":611122,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"煎得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7cad65b9a53d803d4e41f8f991a4f0785b3653","tid":611122,"uid":105075,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"想舊肉多肉汁有好多方法既<br />\n一係浸鹽水，用水浸過雞面，然後用水＋雞淨重加1到2%既鹽浸過夜<br />\n慢煮果陣都可以落小小油落去<br />\n又或者煎之前coat一層麵粉上去<br />\n留意下你樽沙薑有冇鹽係入面<br />\n咁醃法D汁實瀉曬出黎架"},{"pid":"821f810afb3a899f5cd405a1ad490a109c616e31","tid":611122,"uid":146241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8ad893d435c9ea3936dc9bde5155d6e0833cd0","tid":611122,"uid":81698,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"65度45分鐘就夠75度太高<br />\n<br />\n煎果陣壓佢一定流失好多肉汁<br />\n<br />\n最理想係KEEP係袋入面到你搞掂晒D配菜先大火煎雞皮脆身即上<br />\n<br />\nBTW雞脾扒真係唔洗慢煮 是鳩旦煎啦屌<br />\n雞胸就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"我地跟一個慢煮app &quot;joule&quot; 煮<br />\n佢有3 個温度建議<br />\n分別係65, 75, 85<br />\n因為65度有D淆底怕有箘<br />\n所以揀75度"},{"pid":"939643e1034fd258cf7b8570ebebf474ce578b32","tid":611122,"uid":146241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c7cad65b9a53d803d4e41f8f991a4f0785b3653","tid":611122,"uid":105075,"lik